      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d1899e8" class="- topic/p ">Title <ph outputclass="CFR" class="- topic/ph ">48 CFR
9903.201-1 </ph>
            <ph rev="FAC 2021-02 November 23, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2020-003?> <?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 30.201 by removing “(FAR appendix)” twice.?></ph>describes
the rules for determining whether a proposed contract or subcontract
is exempt from CAS. Negotiated contracts not exempt in accordance
with <ph outputclass="CFR" class="- topic/ph ">48 CFR 9903.201-1(b)</ph> shall be
subject to CAS. A CAS-covered contract may be subject to either
full or modified coverage. The rules for determining whether full
or modified coverage applies are in <ph outputclass="CFR" class="- topic/ph ">48 CFR
9903.201-2</ph>.<ph rev="FAC 2021-02 November 23, 2020" class="- topic/ph "> </ph>
